			<h3 ><a href="#p3379" rel="nofollow"><!-- google_ad_section_start -->Re: How I Would Fix the Baltimore Orioles<!-- google_ad_section_end --></a></h3>
			<p class="author"><!-- google_ad_section_start(weight=ignore) --><a rel="nofollow" href="./viewtopic.php?p=3379&amp;sid=fa1aef8b6f2724cee4e657fe32b0f269#p3379"><img src="./styles/static/imageset/icon_post_target.gif" width="11" height="9" alt="Post" title="Post" /></a>Post <a href="./viewtopic.php?p=3379&amp;sid=fa1aef8b6f2724cee4e657fe32b0f269#p3379" onclick="prompt('Direct link to post:',this.href); return false;"><strong>#3</strong></a>&nbsp;by <strong><a href="./memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=2&amp;sid=fa1aef8b6f2724cee4e657fe32b0f269" style="color: #000000;" class="username-coloured">Jordan Tuwiner</a></strong> &raquo; August 7th, 2011, 2:10 pm <!-- google_ad_section_end --></p>

			

